{
  "stem": "16930.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some Jewish children who were in the-- who came to the hostel in '45 from-- who had been in concentration camps, who were also in the-- 14, 15, 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told us about their experiences.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Unbelievable experiences.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how I found out that-- what was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And also, at some point later on, I wrote to the Jewish Kultusgemeinde at someone's advice.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they sent me back that the parents were sent to Opole, which meant that was the last that any records were kept, and the last I guess-- I guess probably within days-- at the most, within weeks-- they were going up in smoke.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And their bodies were made into soap, and maybe the-- the skins into lampshades.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In London, I-- I had this [INAUDIBLE] work in the furniture factory in High Wycombe, I worked in another furniture factory.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got a job in another furniture factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a-- a organization for Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they placed me in a-- in a Jewish home as a-- as a border-- room and board.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Room and board in a Jewish home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember the name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were nice enough people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, is it a kosher home?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The people who told me was like, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's kosher.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they're not religious, but-- they're not-- they're not observant, but they're kosher.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we used to eat there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was another boy also-- also there-- [? there than ?] myself, with these people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was a way people at that point made up the difference of what they needed in income.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The man was-- was an accountant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The woman was a housewife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they needed-- they had bought a house.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
